      "text": "4 hours ago Advertisement BSNL revised its Special Retailer C-Top Up plans (both Prepaid and Postpaid) on PAN India basis. As per the latest information, BSNL will be offering more freebies to those retailers having at least Three SIM activation in a month. Retailers having monthly transaction amount greater than Rs 1000 with at least 'Three SIM' activation may get extra 100 Minutes free off-net voice calls in addition to the existing special concessional tariff of retailer C- Top Up plan In addition, BSNL authorities has also decided to Waive-off C-Top-Up reversal SMS charges of Rs.3/-. For Prepaid C-Top Up Connections, the validity is modified as \"Lifetime\". These connections shall be removed / deleted / disconnected subject to non-fulfillment of condition that \"there should be at least one transaction / recharge in each 90 days\". The above tariff will be implemented with effect from 29-09-2017 on PAN India basis. The implementation of the tariff is to be made in accordance with 43rd Amendment of Telecom Tariff Order and orders/guidelines/clarifications issued by TRAI from time to time. Credit: Keralatelecom...",
